  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the \"<strong>Christmas Store: Santa's Supermarket Simulator</strong>\", you will have to manage the holiday store and make it the perfect place to shop for New Year gifts. Fill the shelves with seasonal goods such as Christmas decorations, presents, and other winter holiday items. Decide which products to stock, set prices, and run promotions to attract customers before the holidays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/b3f5a7ca531f3e18bbe10361d1997b73.poster.avif?t=1755171955\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/b3f5a7ca531f3e18bbe10361d1997b73.webm?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/b3f5a7ca531f3e18bbe10361d1997b73.mp4?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to do?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main task is to manage your resources and staff competently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/f9edfb8b44ac1bea39fce2ffeaa36f71.poster.avif?t=1755171955\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/f9edfb8b44ac1bea39fce2ffeaa36f71.webm?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/f9edfb8b44ac1bea39fce2ffeaa36f71.mp4?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire employees to help with checkout, display goods, and keep the store tidy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/91c30520eb717f0178c66333d6de5cbb.poster.avif?t=1755171955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/91c30520eb717f0178c66333d6de5cbb.webm?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/91c30520eb717f0178c66333d6de5cbb.mp4?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your store to create a winter wonderland atmosphere that will draw in customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/78fd5fe313c4fef1769c70d2671000bf.poster.avif?t=1755171955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/78fd5fe313c4fef1769c70d2671000bf.webm?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/78fd5fe313c4fef1769c70d2671000bf.mp4?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your store by opening new sales areas and improving infrastructure to accommodate more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/db58b1f0215a527d0cd039203e56485e.poster.avif?t=1755171955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/db58b1f0215a527d0cd039203e56485e.webm?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/db58b1f0215a527d0cd039203e56485e.mp4?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your success is measured by how many customers are satisfied and how they feel about your store.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/86942291c310448761cb8ca23331e1cd.poster.avif?t=1755171955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/86942291c310448761cb8ca23331e1cd.webm?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/86942291c310448761cb8ca23331e1cd.mp4?t=1755171955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Put your sales skills to the test, enjoy the festive season, and become the ultimate New Year's store owner in this thrilling and festive game!</strong></p>",
